&lt;p&gt;Applicable system specifications, standards, hardware, software, firmware and test equipment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;119&quot;&gt;
